<L>&para; "What calle &yogh;e &thorn;e Castel," quod I &middot; "&thorn;at kuynde ha&thorn; I-maket,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>&thorn;e</I>] &thorn;at T; &thorn;is U; &thorn;e H<SUB>2</SUB>. <I>ha&thorn;</I>] <I>so in</I> TUH<SUB>2</SUB>; V <I>really has</I> ha&thorn; &thorn;us, <I>but</I> &thorn;us <I>is best omitted</I>.</NOTE></L>
