<L N="28">Fader and Foormere &middot; &thorn;e furste of alle &thorn;ing;<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>&thorn;e</I>] U <I>omits. alle</I>] H<SUB>2</SUB> <I>omits</I>.</NOTE></L>
<L>&THORN;at is &thorn;e grete God &middot; &thorn;at bigynnyng hedde neuere,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>&thorn;at</I>] And &thorn;at TU. <I>is &thorn;e</I>] he is U. <I>bigynnyng</I>] gynnynge TU.</NOTE></L>
