<L N="37">Lyf &thorn;at euer schal lasten &middot; and al his lynage aftur.<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>euer</I>] ay TU. <I>al</I>] U <I>om</I>.</NOTE></L>
<L>&para; &THORN;at is &thorn;e castel &thorn;at kuynde made &middot; <I>Caro</I> hit hette,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>hette</I>] hatte TU; hattith H<SUB>2</SUB>.</NOTE></L>
<L>And is as muche to mene &middot; As Mon wi&thorn; a soule,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>And is</I>] Is U; TH<SUB>2</SUB> <I>omit. to</I>] forto H<SUB>2</SUB>. <I>As</I>] &thorn;at T. <I>a</I>] his T; &thorn;e U.</NOTE></L>
