<L N="84">And alle kunne scolers &middot; In Scoles forte lerne;<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>kunne</I>] kynne U; kynde T. <I>scoles&mdash;lerne</I>] scole to lerne T; scole to lere U.</NOTE></L>
<L>&THORN;enne is Dobet to beo war &middot; for betynge of &yogh;erdes,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Dobet&mdash;war</I>] do-bet to ben ywar T; do-bet ywar H<SUB>2</SUB>; dowel to drede U. <I>&yogh;erdes</I>] &thorn;e &yogh;arde TU.</NOTE></L>
<L>And &thorn;erof sei&thorn; &thorn;e Sauter &middot; &thorn;i-seluen &thorn;ou miht reden,<Q><I>Virga tua</I> [<I>et baculus tuus, ipsa me consolata sunt</I>.]</Q><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>&thorn;erof</I>] &thorn;ere U. <I>&thorn;iseluen</I>] &thorn;e salme TU. <I>The Latin is from</I> TU; V <I>has only</I> virga tua, &amp;c.</NOTE></L>
<L>[Ac &yogh;if clene consience acorde &middot; &thorn;at &thorn;i-selfe dost wel],<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>From</I> T; <I>so also</I> UH<SUB>2</SUB>; V <I>has</I> a <I>corrupt line</I>, Bote Clene Concience a|Corde &middot; Bote &thorn;i-self Dowel. <I>clene</I>] &thorn;i clene U.</NOTE></L>
<L N="88">Wilne &thorn;ou neuere in &thorn;is world &middot; forte Dobetere;<Q>For, <I>Intencio</I> [<I>indicat hominem</I>].</Q><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>forte</I>] why for to UH<SUB>2</SUB>. [<I>indicat hominem</I> TUH<SUB>2</SUB>] V <I>indistinct</I>.</NOTE></L>
<L>&para; Bi Counseil of Concience &middot; a-Cordynge with holy churche,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Bi</I>] Wi&thorn; U. <I>with</I>] of H<SUB>2</SUB>; T <I>omits</I>.</NOTE></L>
<L>Loke &thorn;ou wisse &thorn;i wit &middot; and &thorn;i werkes aftur;</L>
<L>For &yogh;if &thorn;ou comest a&yogh;ein Concience &middot; &thorn;ou Cumbrest &thorn;i|seluen,
<PB REF="00000167.tif" N="115, A-text"></L>
<L N="92">And so witnesse&thorn; Godes Word &middot; And holiwrit bo&thorn;e;<Q>[<I>Qui agit contra conscientiam, edificat ad iehennam</I>.]</Q><NOTE PLACE="foot">T <I>omits, but not</I> H<SUP>2</SUP>. <I>holiwrit bo&thorn;e</I>] holi chirche aftir U. <I>The Latin quotation is from</I> U; TH<SUB>2</SUB> <I>have only the first four words of it</I>.</NOTE></L>
<L>Bote &yogh;if &thorn;ow worche bi godus word &middot; I warne &thorn;e for &thorn;e beste,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>for &thorn;e</I>] &thorn;e T.</NOTE></L>
<L>What so men worden of &thorn;e &middot; wra&thorn;&thorn;e &thorn;e neuere;<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>worden</I>] seyn U.</NOTE></L>
