<L N="97">And beo glad of &thorn;e grace &middot; &thorn;at God ha&thorn; &thorn;e I-sent;<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>&thorn;e Isent</I>] I-sent &thorn;e T; &thorn;e sent U.</NOTE></L>
