<L N="105">&THORN;ruft or &thorn;eodam with hem &middot; selden is I-seye;<Q><I>Qui circuit omne genus,</I> [<I>nullius est generis</I>.]</Q><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>&thorn;eodam</I>] &thorn;edom TU. <I>hem</I>] &thorn;o TU. <I>selden is</I>] is seldom U. [<I>nul|lius&mdash;generis</I>] <I>in</I> U; &amp;c. T; V <I>omits</I>.</NOTE></L>
</LG>
<LG TYPE="stanza">
<L>Poul &thorn;e Apostel &middot; In his pistel wrot<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>wrot</I>] wrot it TU.</NOTE></L>
