<PB REF="00000168.tif" N="116, A-text"><Q>[<I>In ea vocacione qua vocati estis, in eadem perma|neatis</I>].</Q><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>The Latin is from</I> U; T <I>has,</I> In eadem vocacione qua vocati estis, state, &amp;c.; V <I>omits</I>.</NOTE></L>
