<L N="113">Beo payed wi&thorn; &thorn;i porcion &middot; porore or Ricchore.<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>porore&mdash;ricchore</I>] pore o&thorn;er riche T; be it pore or riche U.</NOTE></L>
