<L>&THORN;anne pore peple as plou&yogh;men &middot; and pastours of bestis.'<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>and</I>] or D.</NOTE></L>
<L N="301">Souteris &amp; seweris &middot; suche lewide iottis<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>suche</I>] and swiche U. <I>iottis</I>] Iuttis U.</NOTE></L>
<L>Percen wi&thorn; a pater noster &middot; &thorn;e paleis of heuene,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Percen</I>] Pasen U.</NOTE></L>
<L>Wi&thorn;oute penaunce, at here partynge &middot; in-to hei&yogh;e blisse!<Q><I>Breuis oracio penetrat celum</I>."</Q><NOTE PLACE="foot"><P><I>hei&yogh;e</I>] &thorn;e heye U; the he&yogh;e H<SUB>2</SUB>. <I>Breuis&mdash;celum</I>] UD <I>omit</I>.</P><P>OBS. <I>See</I> Critical Notes <I>as to this ending</I>.</P></NOTE>
</L>
</LG>

