<L>And seiden, "certis sire &middot; cesse shal we neuere</L>
<L N="152">Til Mede be &thorn;i wedded wyf &middot; &thorn;orw wittis of vs alle.<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>&thorn;i wedded</I>] weddid &thorn;i O.</NOTE></L>
