<PB REF="00000310.tif" N="28, B-text"></L>
<L>That she graunteth to gon &middot; with a gode wille,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>she</I>] sho C; heo R. <I>to gon</I>] goo R.</NOTE></L>
