<L N="156">Iugge &yogh;ow ioyntly &middot; in ioye for euere."</L>
<L>&para; Thanne was falsenesse fayne &middot; and fauel as blithe,</L>
<L>And leten sompne alle segges &middot; in schires aboute,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>sompne</I>] somone W. <I>alle</I>] alle &thorn;e R.</NOTE></L>
<L>And bad hem alle be bown &middot; beggeres and othere,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>othere</I>] otheres R.</NOTE></L>
