<L>&para; Ac &thorn;anne cared &thorn;ei for caplus &middot; to kairen hem &thorn;ider,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Ac</I>] And C. <I>kairen</I>] carien W.C.</NOTE></L>
<L>And fauel fette forth &thorn;anne &middot; folus ynowe;<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>folus</I>] foles W; foolis CO.</NOTE></L>
