<L N="211">And gyle do&thorn; hym to go &middot; agast for to dye.</L>
<L>Ac marchantz mette with hym &middot; and made hym abide,<MILESTONE N="9b" UNIT="folio"><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Ac</I>] And C.</NOTE></L>
