<L>And apparailled hym as a prentice &middot; &thorn;e poeple to serue.<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>And</I>] W <I>om. apparailed</I>] apparayleden O. <I>a prentice</I>] Appren|tice W.</NOTE></L>
<L>&para; Li&yogh;tliche lyer &middot; lepe awey &thorn;anne,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>lepe</I>] leep W; leepe O.</NOTE></L>
<L N="216">Lorkynge thorw lanes &middot; to-lugged of manye.<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Lorkynge</I>] Lurkynge W.</NOTE></L>
