<L>If trewthe wil witnesse it be wel do &middot; fortune to folwe,</L>
<L><I>Concupiscencia-carnis</I> &middot; ne coueityse-of-eyes</L>
<L N="40">Ne shal nou&yogh;t greue &thorn;e gretly &middot; ne bigyle &thorn;e, but &thorn;ow wolt."<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>gretly</I>] graythly R. <I>&thorn;e</I> (2)] W <I>om. &thorn;ow wolt</I>] if &thorn;ow wolt &thorn;i-selue W.</NOTE></L>
