<L>&para; Coueityse-of-eyghes &middot; conforted me anon after,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>anon</I>] sone COB.</NOTE></L>
<L>And folwed me fourty wynter &middot; and a fyfte more,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>folwed</I>] folow C. <I>and&mdash;fyfte</I>] or fifty or O; or fifty and CB.</NOTE></L>
<L>&THORN;at of dowel ne dobet &middot; no deyntee me ne &thorn;ou&yogh;te;<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>no</I>] no (<I>printed</I> Ne) W. <I>ne</I> (2)] WCOB <I>om. &thorn;ou&yogh;te</I>] thynke C.</NOTE></L>
<L N="48">I had no lykynge, leue me if &thorn;e leste &middot; of hem au&yogh;te to knowe.<NOTE PLACE="foot">45&mdash;48. R <I>omits.</I></NOTE><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>leue&mdash;leste</I>] ne no luste CB; ne lust O.</NOTE></L>
