<L N="71">"By my feith, frere," quod I &middot; "&yogh;e faren lyke &thorn;ise woweres,</L>
<L>&THORN;at wedde none wydwes &middot; but forto welde here godis;<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>welde</I>] wedden B. <I>godis</I>] goodes WC; goodis B; goed R.</NOTE></L>
