<L>And &thorn;orw &thorn;e wondres of &thorn;is worlde &middot; wytte for to take.<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>wondres</I>] wordes RB. <I>&thorn;is</I>] &thorn;e R.</NOTE></L>
<L>And on a mountaigne &thorn;at mydelerd hy&yogh;te &middot; as me &thorn;o &thorn;ou&yogh;te,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>mydelerd</I>] mydel erde R; myddel er&thorn;e W; midilerd B. <I>&thorn;o</I>] than C; W <I>om.</I></NOTE></L>
