<L>And where &thorn;at bryddes and bestes &middot; by here make[s] &thorn;ei &yogh;eden,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>And</I>] B <I>om.</I> [<I>makes</I> W] make LCRO; mak B; <I>but see</I> l. 335. <I>&thorn;ei</I>] WO <I>om.</I></NOTE></L>
