<PB REF="00000469.tif" N="187, B-text"></L>
<L>In mareys and mores &middot; for men sholde hem nou&yogh;t fynde,</L>
<L N="345">And hudden here egges &middot; whan &thorn;ei &thorn;ere-fro wente,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>hudden</I>] hidden W. <I>egges</I>] egges C; eegis B; eggys O.</NOTE></L>
<L>For fere of other foules &middot; and for wylde bestis.</L>
<L>&para; And some troden her makes &middot; and on trees bredden,</L>
