<L>&para; &THORN;e wyse and &thorn;e witty &middot; wrote &thorn;us in &thorn;e bible,<Q><I>De re que te non molestat, [noli] certare.</I></Q><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>&thorn;e</I> (2)] C <I>om. que te</I>] quiete R. [<I>noli</I> WCOB] noly L; nolite R.</NOTE></L>
