<L N="174">Can nou&yogh;t confourmen a pees &middot; bytwene &thorn;e pope and his enemys,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>&thorn;e pope</I>] W <I>om. cnemys</I>] enmye B; enemye C.</NOTE></L>
