<PB REF="00000503.tif" N="221, B-text"></L>
<L>&THORN;e good wille of a wi&yogh;te &middot; was neure bou&yogh;te to &thorn;e fulle;<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>a</I>] vch a R. <I>neure</I>] nere R.</NOTE></L>
