<L>I haue none gode gyftes &middot; of &thorn;ise grete lordes,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>none</I>] no WO; na C. <I>&thorn;ise</I>] &thorn;is RC.</NOTE>
<PB REF="00000505.tif" N="223, B-text"></L>
<L>For no bred &thorn;at I brynge forth &middot; saue a beneson on &thorn;e sonday,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>brynge</I>] brou&yogh;t R.</NOTE></L>
