<L>So, walde he or nou&yogh;t wolde he &middot; wynnen I wolde;<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>walde he</I>] <I>so in</I> R; wolde he COB; he wolde W. <I>he</I> (2)] R <I>om. nou&yogh;t&mdash;he</I>] he nolde COB.</NOTE></L>
<L>And bothe to kyth and to kyn &middot; vnkynde of &thorn;at ich hadde.</L>
<L>&para; And who so cheped my chaffare &middot; childen I wolde,</L>
