<L>&para; In halydayes at holicherche &middot; whan ich herde masse,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>In</I>] On W. <I>at</I>] in O; and CB. <I>herde</I>] here O.</NOTE></L>
<L>Hadde [I] neuere wille, wot god &middot; witterly to biseche<NOTE PLACE="foot">[<I>I</I> WCOB] LR <I>om.; but the line is marked in</I> L. <I>neuere</I>] nere R.</NOTE></L>
<L N="386">Mercye for my mysdedes &middot; &thorn;at I ne morned more</L>
<L>For losse of gode, leue me &middot; &thorn;an for my lykames giltes<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>For</I>] For (<I>printed</I> Nor) W. <I>my</I>] R <I>om. giltes</I>] gilte CB.</NOTE></L>
<L N="388">As if I had dedly synne done; &middot; I dred nou&yogh;t &thorn;at so sore,<MILESTONE N="57b" UNIT="folio"><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>As</I>] And C. <I>dred</I>] dredde WO; drede CB; dradde R.</NOTE></L>
