<L>&YOGH;e lordes and ladyes &middot; and legates of holicherche,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>&yogh;e</I>] &thorn;e R; <I>also</I> R <I>repeats</I> &thorn;e lordes. <I>cherche</I>] cherches R; kirce C.</NOTE></L>
