<L>Ne no mysproude man &middot; amonges lordes ben allowed.</L>
<L>[&para; Clerkes and kni&yogh;tes &middot; welcometh kynges ministrales,</L>
<L>And for loue of &thorn;e lorde &middot; litheth hem at festes;</L>
<L>Muche more, me thenketh &middot; riche men schulde</L>
<L N="440">Haue beggeres byfore hem &middot; &thorn;e whiche ben goddes ministrales,</L>
