<L>For-thi I rede &yogh;ow riche &middot; reueles whan &yogh;e maketh<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>reueles</I>] at reueles R; <I>but</I> at <I>should probably be omitted, as in</I> MS. Cotton Vesp. B 16.</NOTE></L>
<L>For to solace &yogh;oure soules &middot; suche ministrales to haue;</L>
<L N="444">&THORN;e pore, for a fol sage &middot; syttynge at &thorn;e hey&yogh; table,</L>
