<PB REF="00000516.tif" N="234, B-text"></L>
<L>And fithel &thorn;e, with-out flaterynge &middot; of gode friday &thorn;e storye;</L>
<L N="448">And a blynd man for a bourdeoure &middot; or a bedrede womman,</L>
<L>To crie a largesse by-for oure lorde &middot; &yogh;oure gode loos to schewe!</L>
