<LG TYPE="stanza">
<L>Ac after my wakyng &middot; it was wonder longe,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Ac</I>] As B; An C. <I>wakyng</I>] walkynge RB. <I>wonder</I>] C <I>om.</I></NOTE></L>
