<PB REF="00000622.tif" N="340, B-text"></L>
<L N="372">And be at my biddynge &middot; where so eure me lyketh.</L>
<L>And to be merciable to man &middot; &thorn;anne my kynde it asketh,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>And&mdash;be</I>] Ac R. <I>&thorn;anne&mdash;kynde</I>] my kende &thorn;anne R. <I>it</I>] WO <I>om.</I></NOTE></L>
