<L N="388">And &thorn;ough holiwrit wil &thorn;at I be wroke &middot; of hem &thorn;at deden ille, <Q><I>Nullum malum inpunitum, &amp;c.,</I></Q><NOTE PLACE="foot">386&mdash;388. CB <I>omit.</I></NOTE><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>&thorn;at</I> (1)] R <I>om. Nullum</I>] For nullum O.</NOTE></L>
