<PB REF="00000625.tif" N="343, B-text"></L>
<L N="428">And crepeth to &thorn;e crosse on knees &middot; &amp; kisseth it for a iuwel!<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>crepeth</I>] crepe W. <I>kisseth</I>] kisse W; kisses C.</NOTE></L>
