<L>And gyued me in goutes &middot; I may nou&yogh;te go at large.<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>gyued</I>] gyede O.</NOTE></L>
<L N="192">And of &thorn;e wo &thorn;at I was in &middot; my wyf had reuthe,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>had</I>] hadde (<I>printed</I> hande) W.</NOTE></L>
