<L N="171">Ac reson shal &middot;[rekene] with &yogh;ow &middot; yf ich regne. eny whyle,<NOTE PLACE="foot">[<I>rekene</I>] rekne I; rikene M; regne PEFS; <I>cf.</I> B-text. <I>regne</I>] lyue M. <I>whyle</I>] wyle P.</NOTE></L>
