<L N="174">Ich wolle haue leaute for my lawe; &middot; let be al &yogh;oure ianglyng;<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>let</I>] and late I. <I>al</I>] I <I>om. ianglyng</I> M] ianglend (<I>badly</I>) P; iangle EIFS.</NOTE></L>
