<PB REF="00000919.tif" N="81, C-text"></L>
<L N="182">With-oute mercement o&thorn;er manslauht &middot; amenden alle reames."<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>mercement&mdash;manslauht</I>] man|slau&yogh;t or mercement F.</NOTE></L>
