<L N="158">Han ride out of a-ray &middot; here ruele vuel [y]holde,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>ride</I>] riden F; i-ride M; ridde E. <I>vuel</I>] euel IMF. <I>yholde</I> EG] i-holde MIFS; holde P.</NOTE></L>
