<PB REF="00000929.tif" N="91, C-text"></L>
<L>And priked a-boute on palfrais &middot; fro places to maners,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>priked</I>] i-priked M. <I>fro</I>] to S. <I>to</I> IM] &amp; to ES; in-to P. <I>fro&mdash;maners</I>] to places aboute F.</NOTE></L>
