<L>In places &thorn;er &thorn;ei persons be&thorn; &middot; by hem-self at ese,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>places</I>] place F; many places I. <I>&thorn;ei</I>] &thorn;e I. <I>by</I>] ben M.</NOTE></L>
