<L N="169">Ac &yogh;ut shal come a kyng &middot; and confesse &yogh;ow alle,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Ac &yogh;ut</I>] Ac &thorn;er I; But &yogh;it F; And &yogh;ut M; &YOGH;it &yogh;it (<I>sic</I>) E. <I>kyng</I>] cristene king F. <I>confesse</I>] chastise F.</NOTE></L>
