<L N="192">And sitthen he preide &thorn;e pope &middot; haue pyte of holy|churche,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>sitthen</I>] &thorn;anne F. <I>pope</I>] peple &middot; to M. <I>of</I>] on IMFS.</NOTE></L>
