<DIV3 TYPE="part">
<LG TYPE="stanza">
<L>With &thorn;at ran repentaunce &middot; and reherced hus teme,<MILESTONE UNIT="A page" N="54"><MILESTONE UNIT="B page" N="60"><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>With</I>] Right wi&thorn; I.</NOTE></L>
