<L>Longe was er hue loked vp &middot; and 'lord, mercy,' criede,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Longe</I>] And longe I. <I>was</I>] F <I>om. er</I>] her P; or EMFS; ar I. <I>hue</I>] <I>so</I> S; heo F; &yogh;he I; &yogh;o E; sche M. <I>criede</I>] sche criede M.</NOTE></L>
<L N="5">And by-highte to hym &middot; &thorn;at ous alle made,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>hym</I>] him an hy F.</NOTE></L>
<L>Hue sholde vnsowen hure smok &middot; and sette &thorn;er an heire,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Hue</I>] &thorn;at heo F; &yogh;o E; Sche IM. <I>vnsowen</I> I] vnsowe F; unsewe M; onsewe S; vnsuwe E; vnsywe P. <I>smok</I>] serk IMF; scherte S. <I>&thorn;er</I>] &thorn;eron I; on hure M. <I>an</I>] on S.</NOTE></L>
<L>To afaiten hure flesch &middot; &thorn;at fers was to synne.</L>
<L N="8">"Shal neuere [heigh] herte me hente &middot; bote holde me lowe,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>neuere</I>] no F. [<I>heigh</I> I] hy FS; hi M; hy&yogh; G; my E; myn P; <I>cf.</I> B-text.</NOTE></L>
<L>And suffre to be myssaide &middot; and so dude ich neuere.</L>
<L>Bote now wolle ich meke me &middot; and mercy by-seche<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Bote</I>] &amp; F. <I>wolle ich</I>] i wole M. <I>meke</I>] muke P.</NOTE></L>
<L>Of alle &thorn;at ich haue &middot; yhated in myn herte."<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>alle</I>] alle hem F; alle &thorn;ingus S. <I>yhated</I>] hated IFMS.</NOTE></L>
