<L>Ich was &thorn;e prioresse potager &middot; and o&thorn;er poure ladies,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>prioresse</I>] prioresses MS.</NOTE></L>
<L N="133">And made here ioutes of iangles; &middot; 'dame Iohane was a bastarde,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>here</I>] hem IF. <I>of</I>] wi&thorn; M. <I>iangles</I>] iangelynge IM. <I>dame</I>] &thorn;at dame F. <I>Iohane</I>] ione IFM; Ion S.</NOTE></L>
<L>And dame Clarice a knyghtes douhter &middot; a cokewold was hure syre,</L>
