<L>"Peter!" qua&thorn; a plouhman &middot; and putte forth hus hefd,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>a</I>] S <I>om. hefd</I>] heued IF; heed M; hed E; hese (<I>sic</I>) S.</NOTE></L>
