<L>And maked me sykeren hym sitthen &middot; to seruen hym for euere,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>maked</I>] made EMF; maden SI. <I>hym</I>] I <I>om. seruen</I> ISF] serue MEG; <I>miswritten</I> seren P.</NOTE></L>
