<L N="232">So shalt &thorn;ow come to a court &middot; as cleer so &thorn;e sonne,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>So</I>] And so I. <I>court</I>] cot I. <I>as</I>] so MG. <I>so</I>] as MIS.</NOTE></L>
