<L N="44">He worth ra&thorn;er receyued &middot; and reuerentloker sette;<Q><I>Amice, ascende superius.</I></Q><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>sette</I>] sitte MISG. <I>Amice, &amp;c.</I>] M <I>om.</I></NOTE></L>
