<L>Nameliche atte mete &middot; suche men eschewe;<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Nameliche</I>] Ac nameliche I. <I>atte</I>] at &thorn;e IM; at S. <I>eschewe</I> IMSG] eschywe P; eschiwe E.</NOTE></L>
<L N="52">Hit ben &thorn;e deueles disours &middot; to drawe men to synne.<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Hit&mdash;&thorn;e</I>] For it ben I.</NOTE>
<PB REF="00000980.tif" N="142, C-text"></L>
