<L>"Ich assente, by seynt Gyle" &middot; seyde &thorn;e knyght &thorn;enne,</L>
<L>"For to worche by &thorn;y witt &middot; and my wyf bo&thorn;e."</L>
<L N="56">"Ich shal aparaile me," qua&thorn; perkyn &middot; "in pylgrymes wyse,<MILESTONE UNIT="A page" N="77"><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Ich shal</I>] And I schal I. <I>aparaile</I>] paraile I. <I>in</I>] in a M.</NOTE></L>
