<L>And heng hus hoper on hus hals &middot; in stede of a scrippe;<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>heng</I>] hyng M. <I>in</I>] in &thorn;e M.</NOTE></L>
<L N="61">A boussel of bred-corn &middot; brouht was &thorn;er-ynne.<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>boussel</I>] buschel ESG; busschel M.</NOTE></L>
