<L N="64">My plouh-fot shal be my pyk-staf &middot; and picche a two &thorn;e rotes,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>plouh-fot</I>] plowbat S. <I>picche&mdash;two</I>] putte a-wai M.</NOTE></L>
