<L><I>Deleantur de libro uiuencium</I> &middot; Ich sholde nat dele with hem,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Misarranged in all the copies, which put</I> Deleantur&mdash;uiuen|cium <I>in one line</I>, Ich&mdash;hote&thorn; <I>in a second, and</I> of hem&mdash;scribantur <I>in a third; but see</I> B-text.</NOTE><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>After</I> uiuencium E <I>inserts</I> &amp; cum iustis non scribantur (<I>unneces|sarily</I>). <I>Ich</I>] I ne M. <I>hem</I>] him E.</NOTE></L>
