<HEAD>TESTAMENTUM PETRI PLOUHMAN.</HEAD>
<LG TYPE="stanza">
<L><I>In dei nomine, amen</I> &middot; Ich make hit my-self.</L>
<L N="96">He shal haue my soule &middot; &thorn;at alle soules made,</L>
<L>And defende hit fro &thorn;e feende &middot; and so is my by-leyue,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>fro</I>] as fro I. <I>by-leyue</I>] bileue EM; bileeue I; beleue S.</NOTE></L>
