<PB REF="00000983.tif" N="145, C-text"></L>
<L>With &thorn;e resydue and remenaunt &middot; by &thorn;e rode of lukes,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>With</I>] And with I. <I>and</I>] and &thorn;e IMG. <I>lukes</I>] grace M.</NOTE></L>
