<L>Now perkyn with &thorn;e pilgrimes &middot; to &thorn;e plouh is faren;<NOTE PLACE="foot">Now is perkyn and &thorn;ise pil|grimes &middot; to &thorn;e plogh faren I.</NOTE></L>
<L N="113">To eryen hus half aker &middot; holpen hym menye.<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>hus</I>] &thorn;is I. <I>holpen</I>] helpen IMS.</NOTE></L>
<L>Dykers and deluers &middot; diggeden vp &thorn;e balkes;<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>diggeden</I>] dikked I; dikud S. <I>vp</I>] M <I>om.</I></NOTE></L>
