<L>And somme to plese perkyn &middot; pykede aweye &thorn;e wedes.<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>pykede&mdash;&thorn;e</I>] a-felde pikede I. <I>wedes</I>] rotus S.</NOTE></L>
