<LG TYPE="stanza">
<L>THenne hadde wit a wif &middot; was hote dame studie,<MILESTONE UNIT="A page" N="122"><MILESTONE UNIT="B page" N="143"><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>hote</I>] i-hote M. <I>was hote</I>] men callid here F.</NOTE></L>
