<L N="4">Al starynge dame studie &middot; sterneliche seide,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>starynge</I> IES] staryng MF; star|yenge P. <I>sterneliche</I> IESM] sturne|liche PF. <I>seide</I>] sche seide M.</NOTE></L>
