<L>Thei don bote dreuele &thorn;eron &middot; draf were hem leuere<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>dreuele</I> I] dreuel K; dreuelen E; dryuele F; drauele M; dreuely S; dreuelyn P.</NOTE></L>
