<PB REF="00001067.tif" N="229, C-text"></L>
<L N="237">For yf he be fer &thorn;er-fro &middot; ful ofte hath he drede<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>fer</I>] feer P. <I>hath he</I>] he ha&thorn; I.</NOTE></L>
