<L>For couetyze of &thorn;at catel &middot; to culle hem &thorn;at hit kepe&thorn;;<NOTE PLACE="foot">237&mdash;241. T <I>omits.</I></NOTE><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>&thorn;at</I> (1)] S <I>om. hem</I>] him MFSIK.</NOTE></L>
