<L N="8">In gret pouerte [he] was yput; &middot; a pryns, as hit were,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>In</I>] For in IT. [<I>he</I> MIKFST] PE <I>om. yput</I>] i-put M; put KTFS; putte I. <I>pryns</I>] prisoun M (<I>wrongly</I>).</NOTE></L>
