<L N="36">What one ha&thorn;, what ano&thorn;er ha&thorn; &middot; and what hy hadde bo&thorn;e,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>what</I>] &amp; what S. <I>ano&thorn;er</I>] o&thorn;er MTKF; &thorn;at o&thorn;ur S. <I>ha&thorn;</I>] T <I>om. hy</I>] &thorn;ei MIKTFS.</NOTE></L>
