<PB REF="00001083.tif" N="245, C-text"></L>
<L N="240">To blame hym o&thorn;er to bete hym &thorn;enne &middot; ich halde hit bote synne.<MILESTONE UNIT="A page" N="191"><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>o&thorn;er</I>] K <I>om. hym</I> (2)] M <I>om. halde</I>] ne holde T. <I>bote</I>] but a MS.</NOTE></L>
