<L>"&YOGH;e segge&thorn; so&thorn;, by my soule," qua&thorn; ich &middot; "ich haue seyen hit ofte,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>segge&thorn;</I>] seien M. <I>soule</I>] selfe I. <I>seyen</I>] Isey E; isei&yogh;e MT; y-seie K; sey S.</NOTE></L>
<L N="244">[&THORN;er] smyt no &thorn;ynge so smerte &middot; ne smelle&thorn; so foule<NOTE PLACE="foot">[<I>&THORN;er</I> IMKST] Her PE; <I>cf.</I> B-text. <I>ne</I>] &amp; T.</NOTE></L>
