<L N="4">And wissede &thorn;e ful ofte &middot; what dowel was to mene,</L>
<L>And counsailede &thorn;e for cristes sake &middot; no creature to by-gyle,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>counsailede</I>] i-conseiled M; counsalede P. <I>for</I>] ofte for S.</NOTE></L>
