<L N="12">Ac hit suffise&thorn; to be saued &middot; and to be suche as ich tauhte.<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>saued</I>] i-saued M. <I>and</I>] S <I>om. to</I> (2)] MITK <I>om.</I></NOTE>
<PB REF="00001085.tif" N="247, C-text"></L>
<L>Ac for to louye and lene &middot; and lyue wel and by-leyue,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>and</I> (1)] and to MSK; and for to I. <I>and</I> (2)] an P. <I>lyue</I>] li&thorn;e M. <I>and by-leyue</I>] I beleue I.</NOTE></L>
<L>Ys ycallid <I>caritas</I> &middot; kynde loue in english;<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>ycallid</I>] y-callyd S; ycalid P; ycald EMITK. <I>in</I>] an I; on MKT.</NOTE></L>
<L>And &thorn;at is dobet, yf eny suche be &middot; a blessed man, &thorn;at helpe&thorn;<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>suche</I>] man schulde T.</NOTE></L>
