<L>Ac catel and kynde witt &middot; encombre&thorn; ful menye;<MILESTONE UNIT="A page" N="195"><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>encombre&thorn;</I>] accombre&thorn; I; acombre&thorn; KS; accumbri&thorn; T.</NOTE></L>
