<L>Ac comunliche connynge &middot; and vnkynde rychesse,</L>
<L N="20">As, loreles to be lordes &middot; and lewede men techeres,</L>
<L>And holy churche horen help &middot; auerous and coueytous,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>auerous</I>] &amp; auerous S.</NOTE></L>
<L>Drowe&thorn; vp dowel &middot; and distruye&thorn; dobest.<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Drowe&thorn;</I>] <I>so</I> PKS; Drawe&thorn; E; Drie&thorn; M; Dryue&thorn; T. <I>distruye&thorn;</I>] de|stroye&thorn; IT; distrie&thorn; vp M. <I>dobest</I>] do-bet T.</NOTE></L>
<L>Ac grace is a gras &thorn;er-fore &middot; to don hem eft growe;<NOTE PLACE="foot">T <I>omits. eft</I>] ofte K; oft to S.</NOTE></L>
<L N="24">Ac grace growe&thorn; nat &middot; til [goode wil] gynne reyne,<NOTE PLACE="foot">[<I>goode wil</I> K] goode wille E; goud wille S; <I>better than</I> god wol PI; god wole M; god wile T. <I>The true reading is decided by</I> l. 26. <I>gynne</I>] gunne E; &yogh;iue T; &thorn;at hit M; S <I>om.</I></NOTE></L>
