<L N="32">That wit wexe&thorn; &thorn;er-of &middot; and o&thorn;ere [wyrdes] bo&thorn;e;<Q><I>Uultus huius seculi sunt subiecti uultibus celestibus.</I></Q><NOTE PLACE="foot">[<I>wyrdes</I>] wirdes K; wyrdus S; wordes PEIT (<I>wyrdes</I> = destinies).</NOTE></L>
<L>So grace is a gyfte of god &middot; and kynde witt a chaunce,<NOTE PLACE="foot">29&mdash;33. M <I>omits.</I></NOTE></L>
<L>And cleregye and connyng &middot; of kynde wittes techynge.<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>and</I>] a IST. <I>techynge</I>] tech|inges I.</NOTE></L>
<L>And &yogh;ut is cleregie to comende &middot; for cristes loue, more<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>for</I>] fore PM.</NOTE></L>
