<L N="40">And in sond a sygne wrot &middot; and seide to &thorn;e Iewes,<MILESTONE UNIT="A page" N="197"><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>a</I>] I <I>om.</I></NOTE></L>
<L>'That see&thorn; hym-self synneles &middot; cesse nat, ich hote,<NOTE PLACE="foot">G <I>begins again. cesse</I>] sese IST.</NOTE></L>
