<PB REF="00001087.tif" N="249, C-text"></L>
<L>And thauh men maden bokes &middot; god was here maister,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>And thauh</I>] &THORN;aw M; Al-&thorn;ou&yogh; SKTG. <I>And&mdash;bokes</I>] I <I>om.</I></NOTE></L>
<L>And seynte spirit &thorn;e saumplarie &middot; and seide what men sholde wryte.<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>And</I>] And &thorn;e MSI. <I>spirit</I>] espirit MG; esprit I. <I>&thorn;e saumplarie</I>] heore ensamplarie M. <I>what</I>] &thorn;at M. <I>men</I>] me E.</NOTE></L>
<L>And ryght as syht serue&thorn; a man &middot; to see &thorn;e hye strete,<NOTE PLACE="foot">G <I>omits. And</I>] But M. <I>syht</I>] a si&yogh;ht K. <I>strete</I>] wei&yogh;e M.</NOTE></L>
<L N="49">Ryght so lere&thorn; lettrure &middot; lewede men to reson.<NOTE PLACE="foot">G <I>omits. lere&thorn;</I>] lerne&thorn; M.</NOTE></L>
