<L N="54">The whiche is cofre of cristes tresour &middot; and clerkes kepen &thorn;e keyes,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>The</I>] T <I>om. The whiche</I>] For hit G. <I>is</I>] IK <I>om. cofre</I>] &thorn;e cofre I; &thorn;e coffre T.</NOTE></L>
