<L N="384">And counterpleide&thorn; me, conscience; &middot; nowe kynde me a-venge,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>counterpleide&thorn;</I>] counturpleteth F. <I>kynde</I>] kende T; kyng (!) E.</NOTE></L>
<L>And sende me hap and hele &middot; til ich haue peers plouh|man!"</L>
<L>And suthe he gradde after grace &middot; til ich gan a-wake.<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>suthe</I>] si&thorn; EF; si&thorn;&thorn;e ST; se&thorn;&thorn;e M.</NOTE></L>
<TRAILER><I>Hic explicit passus secundus de dobest.</I><NOTE><I>So</I> P; EMF <I>omit</I> Hic. S <I>has</I>&mdash;Explicit secundus &amp; vltimus de dobest; T <I>has</I>&mdash;Explicit; E <I>adds</I>&mdash;incipit passus tercius (!).</NOTE></TRAILER>
<TRAILER>Explicit Peeres Plouheman, scriptum per Thom. Dankastre.</TRAILER>
</LG>
</DIV2>
</DIV1>
